---
gate: OPEN
requires: [sveltekit, gsap, protocol-v4]
---
# GSAP Level Up Animation

## Objective
Implement dynamic frontend animations when a user gains XP or levels up.

## Tasks
1. Import GSAP into the SvelteKit project.
2. Build a reusable Svelte component or action for a progress bar that animates to the new value.
3. Hook into the response payload from `XPRpcFunctions` to trigger "Level Up" sequences (text explosions, dramatic color changes).
4. Ensure animations are performant and don't block UI state updates.
